<div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto bg-white dark:bg-gray-900 p-3 md:p-6 transition-colors duration-300"
     data-controller="exercise-checker text-toggle font-controls"
     data-text-toggle-target="content"
     data-font-controls-target="content">

  <%= render 'shared/page_header', pagina: @pagina %>

  <div class="space-y-6">

    <!-- Istruzione generale -->
    <p class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200">
      <span class="text-cyan-500">•</span> Risolvi sul quaderno i seguenti problemi.
    </p>

    <!-- Problemi 1-12 -->
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">

      <!-- Colonna sinistra -->
      <div class="space-y-4">

        <!-- Problema 1 -->
        <div class="space-y-2">
          <p class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200">
            <%= numero_esercizio_badge(1) %> Un cartolaio acquista 15 scatole di pastelli, che costano € 2,15 l'una. Qual è la spesa complessiva? Dalla vendita di tutte le scatole ricava € 52,50. Quanto guadagna in tutto?
          </p>
          <div class="flex items-center gap-2 flex-wrap">
            <span class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200">Spesa:</span>
            <input type="text" data-correct-answer="32,25" class="w-16 border-b-2 border-dotted border-gray-400 dark:border-gray-500 text-center font-bold bg-transparent dark:text-white">
            <span class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200">€</span>
            <span class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200 mx-2">|</span>
            <span class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200">Guadagno:</span>
            <input type="text" data-correct-answer="20,25" class="w-16 border-b-2 border-dotted border-gray-400 dark:border-gray-500 text-center font-bold bg-transparent dark:text-white">
            <span class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200">€</span>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Problema 2 -->
        <div class="space-y-2">
          <p class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200">
            <%= numero_esercizio_badge(2) %> Il proprietario di un negozio di arredamento ha acquistato un mobile a € 345. Lo vuole vendere guadagnando € 125. A quale prezzo lo deve mettere in vendita?
          </p>
          <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
            <span class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200">Prezzo vendita:</span>
            <input type="text" data-correct-answer="470" class="w-16 border-b-2 border-dotted border-gray-400 dark:border-gray-500 text-center font-bold bg-transparent dark:text-white">
            <span class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200">€</span>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Problema 3 -->
        <div class="space-y-2">
          <p class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200">
            <%= numero_esercizio_badge(3) %> Il proprietario di un negozio di abbigliamento mette in vendita a € 45 l'una 13 maglie, che aveva pagato € 38 ciascuna. Qual è il guadagno per ogni maglia? E per tutte le maglie?
          </p>
          <div class="flex items-center gap-2 flex-wrap">
            <span class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200">Guadagno unitario:</span>
            <input type="text" data-correct-answer="7" class="w-14 border-b-2 border-dotted border-gray-400 dark:border-gray-500 text-center font-bold bg-transparent dark:text-white">
            <span class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200">€</span>
            <span class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200 mx-2">|</span>
            <span class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200">Guadagno totale:</span>
            <input type="text" data-correct-answer="91" class="w-14 border-b-2 border-dotted border-gray-400 dark:border-gray-500 text-center font-bold bg-transparent dark:text-white">
            <span class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200">€</span>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Problema 4 -->
        <div class="space-y-2">
          <p class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200">
            <%= numero_esercizio_badge(4) %> Alla pasticceria "Angolo dolce" sono state vendute 66 confezioni di biscotti a € 3,75 l'una. Quanto ha ricavato la pasticceria? Se sono stati guadagnati in tutto € 118,90, quanto si era speso per acquistare le confezioni dal fornitore?
          </p>
          <div class="flex items-center gap-2 flex-wrap">
            <span class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200">Ricavo:</span>
            <input type="text" data-correct-answer="247,50" class="w-16 border-b-2 border-dotted border-gray-400 dark:border-gray-500 text-center font-bold bg-transparent dark:text-white">
            <span class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200">€</span>
            <span class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200 mx-2">|</span>
            <span class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200">Spesa:</span>
            <input type="text" data-correct-answer="128,60" class="w-16 border-b-2 border-dotted border-gray-400 dark:border-gray-500 text-center font-bold bg-transparent dark:text-white">
            <span class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200">€</span>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Problema 5 -->
        <div class="space-y-2">
          <p class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200">
            <%= numero_esercizio_badge(5) %> Un fruttivendolo acquista 16 casse di frutta, ciascuna delle quali contiene 26 kg di frutta. Quanti chilogrammi di frutta acquista? Quanto ricaverà dalla vendita, se la frutta viene venduta a € 2,25 al chilogrammo?
          </p>
          <div class="flex items-center gap-2 flex-wrap">
            <span class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200">Kg:</span>
            <input type="text" data-correct-answer="416" class="w-14 border-b-2 border-dotted border-gray-400 dark:border-gray-500 text-center font-bold bg-transparent dark:text-white">
            <span class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200 mx-2">|</span>
            <span class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200">Ricavo:</span>
            <input type="text" data-correct-answer="936" class="w-16 border-b-2 border-dotted border-gray-400 dark:border-gray-500 text-center font-bold bg-transparent dark:text-white">
            <span class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200">€</span>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Problema 6 -->
        <div class="space-y-2">
          <p class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200">
            <%= numero_esercizio_badge(6) %> Questa mattina un fornaio ha venduto 38 focaccine a € 1,60 l'una. Quanto ha ricavato in tutto? Se aveva speso per gli ingredienti di ciascuna € 0,92, quanto ha guadagnato per ogni focaccina?
          </p>
          <div class="flex items-center gap-2 flex-wrap">
            <span class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200">Ricavo:</span>
            <input type="text" data-correct-answer="60,80" class="w-16 border-b-2 border-dotted border-gray-400 dark:border-gray-500 text-center font-bold bg-transparent dark:text-white">
            <span class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200">€</span>
            <span class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200 mx-2">|</span>
            <span class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200">Guadagno unitario:</span>
            <input type="text" data-correct-answer="0,68" class="w-14 border-b-2 border-dotted border-gray-400 dark:border-gray-500 text-center font-bold bg-transparent dark:text-white">
            <span class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200">€</span>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Problema 7 -->
        <div class="space-y-2">
          <p class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200">
            <%= numero_esercizio_badge(7) %> Un contadino vende 160 kg di granturco a € 0,75 il kg e 250 kg di patate a € 1,15 il kg. Quanto ricava complessivamente? Se la sua spesa era stata di € 262, quanto guadagna?
          </p>
          <div class="flex items-center gap-2 flex-wrap">
            <span class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200">Ricavo:</span>
            <input type="text" data-correct-answer="407,50" class="w-16 border-b-2 border-dotted border-gray-400 dark:border-gray-500 text-center font-bold bg-transparent dark:text-white">
            <span class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200">€</span>
            <span class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200 mx-2">|</span>
            <span class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200">Guadagno:</span>
            <input type="text" data-correct-answer="145,50" class="w-16 border-b-2 border-dotted border-gray-400 dark:border-gray-500 text-center font-bold bg-transparent dark:text-white">
            <span class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200">€</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Colonna destra -->
      <div class="space-y-4">

        <!-- Problema 8 -->
        <div class="space-y-2">
          <p class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200">
            <%= numero_esercizio_badge(8) %> Un commerciante compra 65 computer portatili a € 299 ciascuno. Decide di rivenderli a € 387,50 l'uno. Quanto guadagna complessivamente?
          </p>
          <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
            <span class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200">Guadagno:</span>
            <input type="text" data-correct-answer="5752,50" class="w-20 border-b-2 border-dotted border-gray-400 dark:border-gray-500 text-center font-bold bg-transparent dark:text-white">
            <span class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200">€</span>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Problema 9 -->
        <div class="space-y-2">
          <p class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200">
            <%= numero_esercizio_badge(9) %> Un fioraio compra 38 tulipani e 54 rose. Paga i tulipani € 0,35 l'uno e le rose € 0,99 l'una. Quanto spende? Dalla loro vendita ricava complessivamente € 76,15. Quanto guadagna in tutto?
          </p>
          <div class="flex items-center gap-2 flex-wrap">
            <span class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200">Spesa:</span>
            <input type="text" data-correct-answer="66,76" class="w-16 border-b-2 border-dotted border-gray-400 dark:border-gray-500 text-center font-bold bg-transparent dark:text-white">
            <span class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200">€</span>
            <span class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200 mx-2">|</span>
            <span class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200">Guadagno:</span>
            <input type="text" data-correct-answer="9,39" class="w-16 border-b-2 border-dotted border-gray-400 dark:border-gray-500 text-center font-bold bg-transparent dark:text-white">
            <span class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200">€</span>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Problema 10 -->
        <div class="space-y-2">
          <p class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200">
            <%= numero_esercizio_badge(10) %> Un negoziante acquista 12 bicchieri spendendo € 22,80. Se dalla vendita di ciascun bicchiere vuole guadagnare € 3, a quanto deve rivendere ogni bicchiere?
          </p>
          <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
            <span class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200">Prezzo vendita:</span>
            <input type="text" data-correct-answer="4,90" class="w-16 border-b-2 border-dotted border-gray-400 dark:border-gray-500 text-center font-bold bg-transparent dark:text-white">
            <span class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200">€</span>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Problema 11 -->
        <div class="space-y-2">
          <p class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200">
            <%= numero_esercizio_badge(11) %> Una sarta ha ricavato € 702 in tutto vendendo degli abiti a € 78 l'uno. Quanti abiti ha venduto? Per confezionarli aveva acquistato 12 m di stoffa a € 27,50 al metro e 10 m di fodera a € 9,75 al metro. Quanto aveva speso? E quanto ha guadagnato?
          </p>
          <div class="flex items-center gap-2 flex-wrap">
            <span class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200">Abiti:</span>
            <input type="text" data-correct-answer="9" class="w-12 border-b-2 border-dotted border-gray-400 dark:border-gray-500 text-center font-bold bg-transparent dark:text-white">
            <span class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200 mx-2">|</span>
            <span class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200">Spesa:</span>
            <input type="text" data-correct-answer="427,50" class="w-16 border-b-2 border-dotted border-gray-400 dark:border-gray-500 text-center font-bold bg-transparent dark:text-white">
            <span class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200">€</span>
            <span class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200 mx-2">|</span>
            <span class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200">Guadagno:</span>
            <input type="text" data-correct-answer="274,50" class="w-16 border-b-2 border-dotted border-gray-400 dark:border-gray-500 text-center font-bold bg-transparent dark:text-white">
            <span class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200">€</span>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Problema 12 -->
        <div class="space-y-2">
          <p class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200">
            <%= numero_esercizio_badge(12) %> Per la sua bancarella la zia di Alice ha preparato degli orecchini da vendere a € 9,50 il paio. Ne vende 24 paia e, a fine giornata, decide di mettere in vendita le 6 paia rimaste a € 5,95. Qual è il ricavo complessivo? La spesa per confezionare tutti gli orecchini era stata di € 160,99. Quanto ha guadagnato?
          </p>
          <div class="flex items-center gap-2 flex-wrap">
            <span class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200">Ricavo:</span>
            <input type="text" data-correct-answer="263,70" class="w-16 border-b-2 border-dotted border-gray-400 dark:border-gray-500 text-center font-bold bg-transparent dark:text-white">
            <span class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200">€</span>
            <span class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200 mx-2">|</span>
            <span class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200">Guadagno:</span>
            <input type="text" data-correct-answer="102,71" class="w-16 border-b-2 border-dotted border-gray-400 dark:border-gray-500 text-center font-bold bg-transparent dark:text-white">
            <span class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200">€</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <%= render 'shared/exercise_controls' %>
  </div>
</div>
